snippet.textDisplay:
I have a rule with things like paracetamol and ibuprofen when I'm sick. I don't take it unless I need to go to the store (because my mom thinks it's appropriate that I go out in public if I have the flu... even though she is a nurse and knows the risks of me spreading it.) Or, if my fever reaches above 40°C. I will always do my best to let my body do its work, but sometimes I dont feel like having fever hallucinations and dreams.
Hydration and sleep will usually do a lot to keep my temperature down, but sometimes it just spikes and I have to take precautions to not overheat and die.
